title: what is the font for this logo i dont know any more details about it
author: sidneyvan94

comments.content:
Small scale and no distinctive letters.  
Following would work as a substitute  
Egyptian Slate Std Black [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/mti/egyptian-slate/](http://web.archive.org/web/20140725005237/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/mti/egyptian-slate/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/mti/egyptian-slate/")  
Alternatives include  
Neutraface Slab Bold [http://www.houseind.com/fonts/neutrafaceslab](http://web.archive.org/web/20140725005237/http:/www.houseind.com/fonts/neutrafaceslab "http://www.houseind.com/fonts/neutrafaceslab")  
Sanchez Condensed Black [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/latinotype/sanchez-condensed/](http://web.archive.org/web/20140725005237/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/latinotype/sanchez-condensed/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/latinotype/sanchez-condensed/")  
Serifa 75 Black  
 [http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/serifa/](http://web.archive.org/web/20140725005237/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/serifa/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/serifa/")
